 <br/><a name='toc_1'></a>
<h1 class='doclevel'>1.Test Suite : psir3591_BBT</h1>
<div><p>Se testeaza updatarea unui Produs.</p>
</div><a name="toc_tc29553"></a><p>&nbsp;</p><div> <table class="tc" width="90%" ><tr><th colspan="4">Test Case P235-37: UpdatareProdusTestCase01&nbsp;<span style="font-size: 80%;">[Version  : 1]</span></th></tr>
<tr><td width="20%" valign="top"><span class="label">Author:</span></td><td colspan="3">psir3591</td></tr>
<tr><td colspan="4"><span class="label">Summary:</span><br /><p>ECP Pret Valid</p>

<p>Se updateaza pretul unui produs care exista deja.</p>

<p>Pretul introdus este mai mare ca 0 si produsul ar trebuii sa fie updatat.&nbsp;</p>
</td></tr><tr><td colspan="4"><span class="label">Preconditions:</span><br /><p>Pret &gt; 0</p>
</td></tr><tr><td width="20%" valign="top"><span class="label">Execution type:</span></td><td colspan="3">Manual</td></tr>
<tr><td width="20%" valign="top"><span class="label">Estimated exec. duration (min):</span></td><td colspan="3"></td></tr>
<tr><td width="20%" valign="top"><span class="label">Importance:</span></td><td colspan="3">Medium</td></tr>
<tr><td colspan="4"></td></tr><tr><td > name of the autotest class:</td><td  colspan = "3" >UpdateProductServiceTest</td></tr>
<tr><td > name of the test method:</td><td  colspan = "3" >ShouldUpdateProduct_WhenPriceIsValid</td></tr>
<tr><td width="20%" valign="top"><span class="label">Requirements</span><td colspan="3">psir3591_F01:  UpdatareProdus [Version : 1]<br /></td></tr>
<tr><td width="20%" valign="top"><span class="label">Keywords:</span></td><td colspan="3">&nbsp;None<br/></td></tr>
</table>
</div>
<a name="toc_tc29555"></a><p>&nbsp;</p><div> <table class="tc" width="90%" ><tr><th colspan="4">Test Case P235-38: UpdatareProdusTestCase02&nbsp;<span style="font-size: 80%;">[Version  : 1]</span></th></tr>
<tr><td width="20%" valign="top"><span class="label">Author:</span></td><td colspan="3">psir3591</td></tr>
<tr><td colspan="4"><span class="label">Summary:</span><br /><p>ECP Pret Invalid</p>

<p>Se updateaza pretul unui produs care exista deja.</p>

<p>Pretul introdus este mai mic sau egal cu 0 si ar trebuii sa fie aruncata o exceptie.</p>
</td></tr><tr><td colspan="4"><span class="label">Preconditions:</span><br /><p>Pret &lt;= 0</p>
</td></tr><tr><td width="20%" valign="top"><span class="label">Execution type:</span></td><td colspan="3">Manual</td></tr>
<tr><td width="20%" valign="top"><span class="label">Estimated exec. duration (min):</span></td><td colspan="3"></td></tr>
<tr><td width="20%" valign="top"><span class="label">Importance:</span></td><td colspan="3">Medium</td></tr>
<tr><td colspan="4"></td></tr><tr><td > name of the autotest class:</td><td  colspan = "3" >UpdateProductServiceTest</td></tr>
<tr><td > name of the test method:</td><td  colspan = "3" >ShouldThrowException_WhenPriceIsInvalid</td></tr>
<tr><td width="20%" valign="top"><span class="label">Requirements</span><td colspan="3">psir3591_F01:  UpdatareProdus [Version : 1]<br /></td></tr>
<tr><td width="20%" valign="top"><span class="label">Keywords:</span></td><td colspan="3">&nbsp;None<br/></td></tr>
</table>
</div>
<a name="toc_tc29557"></a><p>&nbsp;</p><div> <table class="tc" width="90%" ><tr><th colspan="4">Test Case P235-39: UpdatareProdusTestCase03&nbsp;<span style="font-size: 80%;">[Version  : 1]</span></th></tr>
<tr><td width="20%" valign="top"><span class="label">Author:</span></td><td colspan="3">psir3591</td></tr>
<tr><td colspan="4"><span class="label">Summary:</span><br /><p>BVA Pret Limita Inferioara Valida</p>

<p>Se updateaza pretul unui produs care exista deja.</p>

<p>Pretul introdus este mai mare ca 0 (0.01 care se afla peste limita inferioara) si ar trebuii sa se updateze produsul.</p>

<p>&nbsp;</p>
</td></tr><tr><td colspan="4"><span class="label">Preconditions:</span><br /><p>Pret = 0.01</p>
</td></tr><tr><td width="20%" valign="top"><span class="label">Execution type:</span></td><td colspan="3">Manual</td></tr>
<tr><td width="20%" valign="top"><span class="label">Estimated exec. duration (min):</span></td><td colspan="3"></td></tr>
<tr><td width="20%" valign="top"><span class="label">Importance:</span></td><td colspan="3">Medium</td></tr>
<tr><td colspan="4"></td></tr><tr><td > name of the autotest class:</td><td  colspan = "3" >UpdateProductServiceTest</td></tr>
<tr><td > name of the test method:</td><td  colspan = "3" >ShouldUpdateProduct_WhenPriceIsOverTheLowerBoundary</td></tr>
<tr><td width="20%" valign="top"><span class="label">Requirements</span><td colspan="3">psir3591_F01:  UpdatareProdus [Version : 1]<br /></td></tr>
<tr><td width="20%" valign="top"><span class="label">Keywords:</span></td><td colspan="3">&nbsp;None<br/></td></tr>
</table>
</div>
<a name="toc_tc29559"></a><p>&nbsp;</p><div> <table class="tc" width="90%" ><tr><th colspan="4">Test Case P235-40: UpdatareProdusTestCase04&nbsp;<span style="font-size: 80%;">[Version  : 1]</span></th></tr>
<tr><td width="20%" valign="top"><span class="label">Author:</span></td><td colspan="3">psir3591</td></tr>
